Package: nhanesdata
Title: An R Package to Access and Manage NHANES Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Kyle", "Grealis",
           email = "kyle@kylegrealis.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3550-9749"))
Description: A set of tools to download, process, and store data from the
    National Health and Nutrition Examination Survey (NHANES). It provides
    wrapper functions to the 'nhanesA' package to download data across
    multiple survey cycles and helper functions to read data from a public
    data store.
